des:
Medical providers at IndyCare are dedicated to helping you and your family feel better. Come to our health and wellness center for minor injuries and illnesses or routine physicals and other health services. We offer treatments for many services.

Here's our location:
110 Boone Square St, #29A
Hillsborough, NC 27278

Phone: (919) 245-1213

Our skill will allow you to request appointments from our office, as well as get all the latest promotions we have going on!
